'''2015年華盛頓州野火'''，是指自2015年6月28日起迄今在[[美國|美國]][[華盛頓州|華盛頓州]]所發生的多起[[森林火災|森林火災]]。{{as of|2015|8|21|df=us}}，已有多達3000名[[消防隊員|消防隊員]]被部署投入救火工作中；而火災已燒毀了超過{{convert|600000|acres|sqkm}}的[[林地|林地]]。<ref name="fox" /><ref name=Komos>{{cite news |date=August 21, 2015 |title=Wildfires explode in size as high winds blast region |url=http://www.komonews.com/news/local/Mother-of-fallen-firefighter-He-was-the-center-of-our-lives-322513441.html |work=[[KOMO-TV|KOMO-TV]] |accessdate=August 22, 2015 |archive-date=2015-12-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151220102826/http://www.komonews.com/news/local/Mother-of-fallen-firefighter-He-was-the-center-of-our-lives-322513441.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

8月21日，總統[[贝拉克·奥巴马|贝拉克·奥巴马]]宣佈因此次火災，華盛頓州進入[[緊急狀態|緊急狀態]]<ref name="RT America" />；且因為此次火災的嚴重程度，官員也要求當地居民自願協助救火，這也是該州歷史上的首次<ref name="RT America">{{cite news |date=August 21, 2015 |title=Washington recruits volunteer firefighters as wildfires declared federal emergency |url=https://www.rt.com/usa/313078-washington-wildfires-volunteers-federal-emergency/ |work=[[RT_(TV_network)|RT]] |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150823222026/https://www.rt.com/usa/313078-washington-wildfires-volunteers-federal-emergency/ |archivedate=2015年8月23日 |accessdate=August 23, 2015 }}</ref>。而8月24日的{{link-en|奧卡諾根縣火災|Okanogan Complex fire}}，也成為州史上規模最大的森林火災<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/british-columbia/okanogan-complex-fire-the-largest-in-washington-state-history-1.3201906 |title=Okanogan Complex fire the largest in Washington state history |publisher=[[CBC_News|CBC News]] |date=August 25, 2015 |accessdate=August 26, 2015 |author=The Associated Press |location=[[Ottawa,_Ontario|Ottawa, Ontario]] |archive-date=2015-08-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150828172830/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/british-columbia/okanogan-complex-fire-the-largest-in-washington-state-history-1.3201906 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

根據在[[博伊西|博伊西]]的{{link-en|國家林火協調中心|National Interagency Fire Center}}所提供的[[資訊|資訊]]<ref name="NIFC">{{cite web |url=http://www.nifc.gov/fireInfo/nfn.htm |title=Current Fire Information |work=National Interagency Fire Center |date=August 25, 2015 |accessdate=August 26, 2015 |archive-date=2015-09-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150903031820/http://www.nifc.gov/fireInfo/nfn.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，至8月25日，全美國有11州，共66起大型的森林火災仍在持續中，合計已燒毀超過160萬英畝的林地<ref name="NIFC" />，包括華盛頓州、[[爱达荷州|爱达荷州]]、[[俄勒冈州|俄勒冈州]]、[[蒙大拿州|蒙大拿州]]和[[加利福尼亞州|加利福尼亞州]]等[[美國西部|美國西部]][[乾旱|乾旱]]區的29,000名消防員正與大火搏鬥 <ref name=Komos />；在華盛頓州的12起大型森林火災，最終導致{{convert|709,246|acres|sqkm}}的林地被燒毀，但已無新的火災發生<ref name="NIFC" />。

8月25日，駐紮在[[路易斯–麥克喬德聯合基地|路易斯–麥克喬德聯合基地]]，[[美國陸軍|美國陸軍]]{{link-en|第17野戰砲兵旅 (美國)|17th Field Artillery Brigade (United States)|第17野戰砲兵旅}}的2000名軍人，已被部署加入救火<ref name="NIFC" />；而在華盛頓州，已有4,000名應募的志願者投入協助工作<ref name="Daily Mail">{{cite web |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3209911/Washington-wildfires-worst-state-s-history-firefighters-travel-Australia-New-Zealand-help-battle-blaze.html |title=Washington wildfires the 'worst in the state's history' as firefighters travel from Australia and New Zealand to help battle the blazes |date=August 25, 2015 |accessdate=August 26, 2015 |author=Darren Boyle |publisher=[[Daily_Mail|Daily Mail]] |location=UK |archive-date=2015-08-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150825164007/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3209911/Washington-wildfires-worst-state-s-history-firefighters-travel-Australia-New-Zealand-help-battle-blaze.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

